snippet.title: Samबहादुर - Official Trailer | Vicky Kaushal | Meghna Gulzar | Ronnie S | In Cinemas 01.12.2023
snippet.description:
To the Indian army, to the nation and its people, we present to you a glimpse into the life of India's Greatest Soldier, Sam Manekshaw. 

#SamBahadur Trailer Out Now! 
#Samबहादुर in cinemas 1.12.2023

#SamIsHere 

Samबहादुर is a tribute to Field Marshal Sam HFJ Manekshaw, MC, India's first Field Marshal and a legendary Army General. His career witnessed the shaping of India's geopolitical borders, and his life was marked by significant milestones, from fighting in World War II to being the Chief of Army Staff during the 1971 Indo-Pakistan war, that led to the creation of Bangladesh.
This RSVP film explores his dynamic personality and his unparalleled military career, offering a glimpse into the life of a no-nonsense Army Commander, also known as "Sam Bahadur" by the soldiers he led.

snippet.title: IND Beat SA: Kohli's Triple Blast, Shoaib Akhtar Shocked! | Aakash Chopra Reaction | World Cup 2023
snippet.description:
India Beats South Africa World Cup 2023 Live Updates: In the match played between India and South Africa in the World Cup 2023, India has defeated South Africa. Batting first, Team India had given a target of 327 runs to South Africa to win. In response to which South African team was out within 100 runs. Kohli played a century for India. Shreyas Iyer played an inning of 77 runs. On the bowling front, Ravindra Jadeja took 5 wickets and Kuldeep took 2 wickets. The entire South African team could score only 83 runs. The 243-run victory, which came on the occasion of Virat Kohli's birthday, was spectacular.

snippet.description:

Jethalal is giving sweets to everyone in Gokuldham after this 1000 phone incident. Now Jethalal is going to Babita ji. Stay tuned.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 2724
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 382
snippet.description:
എന്തോ കാര്യമായി അന്വേഷിക്കുകയാണ് ലെച്ചു. അന്വേഷിച്ചു ചെന്നപ്പോൾ തനിക്ക് പ്രയോജനമില്ലാത്തതൊന്നും കൈകൊണ്ട് തൊടില്ലെന്നു ബാലു. ലെച്ചുവിന് ഇത്രയും വേണ്ടപ്പെട്ട വസ്തു കൈക്കലാക്കിയതാര്? അറിയുവാൻ മറക്കാതെ കാണുക, 'ഉപ്പും മുളകും'.  

Lechu is searching for something very important. When checked with Balu, he says he wouldn't touch anything that is of no use to him. Who has hidden the thing Lechu is looking for? To find out, watch 'Uppum Mulakum'

snippet.title: कौन है Bhide की ये हालत का जिम्मेदार? |  Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | 4 Nov 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Tapu Sena plans to play night cricket. Bapuji has told Tapu not to trouble anyone. Tapu is angry at Goli's brother. Goli's brother has come to play cricket with them.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 0175
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 


About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

Lyrics - 

लड़की:- खा ल दही पिया,लागी सही पिया
काहे करे ल तू नहीं नहीं पिया(कितना मानती हो यार)
लड़का:- अतना मनबु त जाइब मोटाई हो दादा
कोरस:- मुँह छोटा बा कइसे घोंटाई हो दादा
आई हो दादा आरे आई हो दादा
 मेहरी मिलल बिया हमरा के गाई हो दादा
कोरस:- दुनो बेरा तू बना के पिय चाई हो दादा


लड़का:- मिलत खीरे बा हो, आ पनीरे बा हो
अइसन वाइफ से लाइफ अमीरे बा हो
कोरस:- भगवान के लिखल तकदीरें बा हो
लड़की:- बोल बोल का ख़ईब ए सइयां 
लिआई नमकीन की मिठईया
लड़का:- तोहार चुम्मा लागेला मिठाई हो दादा
कोरस:- भउजी फेल भइले सब हलुआई हो दादा
लड़का:- आई हो दादा आरे आई हो दादा
 मेहरी मिलल बिया हमरा के गाई हो दादा


लड़का:- माने आशु के हो प्रियांशु के हो
ई त जान हिय पवन व्यासु के हो
कोरस:- ई त गोड़वा दबावे ली सासु के हो
लड़की:- पिया आई थाकल बानी रउआ 
लगाई दिही तेल गमकउआ
लड़का:- देलु मरद के दरद भगाई हो दादा
कोरस:- तोहार बोलिये लागेला दवाई हो दादा
आई हो दादा आरे आई हो दादा
 मेहरी मिलल बिया हमरा के गाई हो दादा

Today’s recipe is Diwali faral shankarpali using 1 kilo maida. It turns out nice, crispy and flaky. Diwali faral is incomplete without shankarpali. We already have seen different recipes if shankarpali. This is full proof recipe the proportion used is just perfect. It is a very easy and simple recipe. You can make it within no time. Besides, I am sharing few tips to make perfect shankarpali. This is a popular Marathi recipe. Also it can be a good tea time snack. You can try this recipe at home and drop a comment for me. Do not forget to like, share and subscribe.

Ingredients:
• 1 cup Milk
• 1 cup Sugar
• 1 cup Ghee
• 7 cups / 1 kilo Maida
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and add milk and sugar. 
• Heat it up together until sugar is dissolved. 
• When sugar is dissolved and the mixture begins to boil, turn off the gas and add ghee. 
• Melt ghee before measuring. Make sure you don’t use thick ghee. 
• Mix well and base for shankarpali is ready. 
• Transfer the base into the maida and mix in with the help of ladle. 
• Knead the mixture into dough. 
• Make small portions of the dough. Keep the leftover dough covered with a wet cloth.
• Take one portion and roll it into a thick chapati. The thickness of the chapati should be about 1 
  cm. 
• Cut off the edges and roll the chapati little more if you want. 
• Cut shankarpali into size and shape you want and take them out into a dish. 
• Rolled out shankarpali should not dry out. 
• Heat up oil on high heat for about 5 minutes and reduce the heat to low. 
• Drop shankarpali into hot oil and fry it well for at least 3-4 minutes. 
• If oil is hot enough and still shankarpali dissolves in oil, then add a little more maida into the 
  dough. Add a little milk and knead the dough again. Roll out shankarpali and fry. It won’t dissolve. 
• When shankarpali gets nice golden color from all sides, take it out, drain excess oil and transfer it 
  into a dish. Shankarpali is ready.
• You can store them in an air tight container when they cool down completely. They have shelf life 
  of about 1 month.

snippet.title: Jethalal ने की एक Pani Puri वाले से कैसी Deal? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chasmah | Pani Puri
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Bagha and Nattu Kaka try to convince Jethalal to follow their tips to grow the sales of Gada Electronics. Jethalal visits a Pani Puri Shop, recommended by Nattu Kaka. Jetha likes the Pani Puri a lot and wants to do a deal with him. Watch the full episode. 

Show Name : Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Kush Shah, Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 2571
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#comedy2023 #comedy #jethalal #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch the specially curated series of Pani Puri:
https://studio.youtube.com/playlist/PLSXTaG1fT0cQEuCKKlujcVJPbbmUKJMKD/edit

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 381
snippet.description:
സ്വന്തമായി വീട് ഇല്ലാത്തതിനെ കുറിച്ചുള്ള ചർച്ചയിലാണ് ലച്ചുവും, കേശുവും, ശിവാനിയും, പാറുവും. പത്താം ക്ലാസ്സിൽ മുഴുവൻ മാർക്കും വാങ്ങി സ്വന്തം വീട്ടിൽ കയറണം എന്നതാണ് ശിവാനിയുടെ ആഗ്രഹം. മക്കളുടെ ചോദ്യങ്ങൾക്കു മുൻപിൽ നിസ്സഹായരായി ബാലുവും നീലുവും!

Lachu, Keshu, Shivani and Paru are having a discussion on not having a house of their own. Shivani's biggest dream is to step into her own house after scoring flashy marks in tenth grade. Balu and Neelu seem to be helpless when confronted by their children!

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3921 | 6 Nov 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3921: Chand Par Padosi
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha eventually sees Mr. Chand and talks about the lunar plot and how to buy it without any complications. Mr. Chand explains to Jetha the high demand in society for a lunar plot. He claims that high-profile political figures and movie actors want to acquire property on the Moon. Jetha is taken in by his words and promptly books three plots. Bagha and Nattu Kaka are overjoyed by the news, but how will Champaklal react? Watch the episode to find out what happens when Jetha tells his father about his newly purchased property.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3921, 6 Nov 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.description:

Mannat Murad Episode 12 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 6th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

#chakalirecipe #madhurasrecipe #bhajnichakli

Ingredients:
Bhajani
• 2 1/2 cup / 500 gm Rice
• 1 cup / 200 gm Chana dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Moong dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Urad dal
• 1/2 cup / 100 gm Poha
• 20 gm Coriander seeds
• 20 gm Cumin seeds
Chakali
• 3 cups Water
• 1/4 cup Oil
• 1 tsp Oil
• 1 tsp Red chili powder
• Salt to taste
• 1 tbsp Coriander powder
• 1 kilo Chakali bhajani
• 1 tsp Ajwain / Carom seeds
• 1 tsp white Sesame seeds
• Oil for frying

Method:
• Wipe the rice really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe chana dal really good with clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe moong dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• Wipe urad dal really good with a clean wet cotton cloth. 
• You can wash and dry all these ingredients if you want. 
• Heat up a pan on medium heat and roast rice really good. 
• The rice should be roasted well but the color should not change. 
• When the rice is roasted well take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast chana dal really good until it begins to get reddish color and take it out into 
  a dish. 
• In the same pan roast moong dal well until it gets reddish color and take it out into a dish. 
• In the same pan roast urad dal really good until it gets light golden color and take it out into a 
  dish. 
• Roast poha really good and transfer them into the dish. 
• In the same pan roast coriander seeds and cumin seeds together on low heat until nice aroma 
  begins to release from it and transfer it into the dish. 
• Mix everything well together and let it cool down. 
• Grind it from the mill. Make sure that it is ground after rice or jawar is ground and not after wheat. 
• Blend it into flour in mixer and sieve it through flour strainer. 
• Blend the leftover coarse flour in the strain again in blender and sieve it. Bhajani for chakali is 
  ready.
Chakali
• Heat up water in a pan and add oil. 
• Mix well and add red chili powder, salt, coriander powder. 
• Mix well and when the mixture boils really good, reduce the heat to low. 
• Add the bhajani flour and turn off the gas. 
• Add carom seeds, sesame seeds and mix everything well together quickly. 
• Transfer the ukad into a dish and knead dough. If needed use very little hot water. 
• Knead the ukad really good when it is still hot. The consistency of the dough should be stiff. 
• Take small portion from the dough and knead it really good again. 
• Make a smooth and even roll and transfer it into chakali machine. 
• Press the dough well and roll out chakali from it on a butter paper. 
• Seal both the ends of the chakali really good. 
•You can use plastic sheet or dish in place of butter paper. 
• Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
• If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
• Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
• When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
• When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
• Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready. 

For more Such Recipes

• Heat up oil in a pan on medium to high heat for about 6-7 minutes and drop a small chakali in it. 
• If it is fried well, then the oil is hot enough. 
• Drop chakali into hot oil and fry well. 
• When the chakali begins to settle at the bottom, flip it over and fry well from other side too. 
• When chakali begins to settle at the bottom of the pan, it means it is fried well from both sides. 
• Take the chakali out, drain excess oil and transfer it into a dish. Chakali is ready. 

For more Such Recipes

snippet.title: Unlocking the Secrets of the Malik Family | LOL PODCAST |
snippet.description:
"LOL Podcast के इस खास एपिसोड में, हम जानेंगे अरमान मलिक, कृतिका मलिक, और पायल मलिक की अद्वितीय प्रेम कहानी के बारे में। अरमान ने कृतिका और पायल के साथ शादी की है, और वे सबकुछ साझा करके खुश और सफल जीवन बिता रहे हैं। हम साथ चलें और जानें उनके असामान्य रिश्ते, उन्होंने कैसे समस्याओं का सामना किया, और उनके पॉपुलर YouTube चैनल्स के पीछे के राज। समझें कैसे उन्होंने समाजिक नियमों को तोड़कर प्यार और खुशी पाई, और सफल सामग्री निर्माणकर्ता के रूप में उनके प्रेरणास्पद सफर के बारे में। इस दिलचस्प एपिसोड को ना देखने पर, प्यार की सभी रूपों की प्रशंसा करने वाला मौका न गवाएं।"

In this special episode of Bharti TV we delve into the extraordinary love story of Arman Malik, Kritika Malik, and Payal Malik,  Arman is married to both Kritika and Payal, and they're living a happy and successful life together. Join us as we explore their unconventional relationship, the challenges they've faced, and the secrets behind their thriving YouTube channels. Discover how they've defied societal norms to find love and happiness, and learn about their inspiring journey as successful content creators. Don't miss this fascinating episode that celebrates love in all its forms. 

bhartisingh #harshlimbachiya #armaanmalik #payalmalik #kritikamalik #chirayumalik #vlog

snippet.title: आधे से भी कम दाम पर प्याज बेच रही मोदी सरकार
snippet.description:
#onion #centralgovernment #onionpricehike #onionprices #pricehike 
केंद्र सरकार ने लोगों को त्योहार के मौके पर सस्ता प्याज उपलब्ध कराने के लिए शहरों में 25 रुपये प्रति किलोग्राम के रियायती रेट पर प्याज बेचना भी शुरू कर दिया है। हालांकि सरकार ने अगले सप्ताह कर्नाटक, महाराष्ट्र व आंध्र प्रदेश से प्याज की नई फसल मार्केट में आने के बाद दामों में गिरावट आने की संभावना जताई है।

बिजनेस जगत की हर बड़ी खबर, उनसे जुड़े एक्सप्लेनर वीडियो, बिजनेस शख्सियत  की दिलचस्प कहानियां, रियल एस्टेट, गोल्ड, ऑटो सेक्टर, स्टार्टअप्स,  शेयर बाजार, सेंसेक्स और पर्सलन फाइनेंस जैसे विषयों की जानकारी हासिल करने के लिए जुड़े बिजनेस टुडे हिंदी से। यहां आपकों म्यूचुअल फंड, एसआईपी, इक्विटी, बीमा, लोन्स, पेंशन, रिटायरमेंट योजनाओं के बारे में आसान भाषा में मिलेगी दिलचस्प जानकारी। 

आप हमें यहां फॉलो कर सकते हैं: 

वेबसाइट: https://www.bazaar.businesstoday.in 

फेसबुक: https://www.facebook.com/businesstodaybazaar

ट्विटर:  https://twitter.com/BT_Bazaar

इंस्टाग्राम: https://www.instagram.com/bt_bazaar/

Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Maa Nahi Saas Hoon Main Episode 05 - [Eng Sub] - Hammad Shoaib - Sumbul Iqbal - Farhan Ally Agha - 7th November 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

This story revolves around Mehreen and her daughter Areej, who was born after years of prayers. Prior to her birth, Mehreen and her husband had been caring for Salman, Areej's cousin. However, a tragedy struck, separating Areej from her family. Afterwards, Mehreen decided to raise Salman as her own son.
Years later, Salman crosses paths with Urooj, a beautiful and fearless girl, the daughter of school teacher Shoaib and his wife Naseem. Initially resistant to Salman's advances, Urooj eventually falls in love with him. Unbeknownst to Salman and his family, Urooj is none other than Areej, Mehreen's long-lost daughter.
Will Urooj discover the truth about her identity? How will the family come to know that Urooj is Mehreen’s long-lost daughter, Areej? How will Urooj react when she gets to know that Mehreen is her real mother? What impact will Urooj’s identity have on Salman? Will Mehreen accept Urooj as her daughter? Will Urooj’s true identity pose a threat to her relationship with Salman?

Written By: Sajjad Haider Zaidi & Abu Rashid
Directed By: Saleem Ghanchi
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

snippet.title: 1/2 kg बेसनाचे लाडू दाणेदार, न बसणारे होण्यासाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | असे ओळखा तुपाचे प्रमाण Besan Ladu
snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.
सरिताज किचनचे प्रॉडक्ट्स | Saritas Kitchen Products -
 1. सर्व प्रकारची लाकडी घाणा तेलं | All Types of Wood Pressed Oils
 2. डंकावर कुटून केलेला कांदा लसूण मसाला | Handmade Kanda Lasun Masala
 3. सरिताज किचन सेंद्रिय गुळ | Chemical free Jaggery cubes and powder 
 4. सेंधव मीठ | Pink Himalayan Salt
 5. सेंद्रियहळद | Organic Turmeric
ऑर्डर करण्यासाठी | To Order -
 • Website - https://saritaskitchenofficial.com/
 • Amazon - http://bitly.ws/zDuc

1/2 kg बेसनाचे लाडू दाणेदार, न बसणारे होण्यासाठी या 10 चुका टाळा | असे ओळखा तुपाचे प्रमाण Besan Ladu

बेसन लाडू 
बेसन लाडू रेसिपी | दिवाळी सणानिमित्त खास लाडू रेसिपी | सोपे व झटपट होणारे बेसन लाडू | दिवाळी फराळ रेसिपी | दिवाळी स्पेशल लाडू रेसिपी | लाडू व  बेसन भाजण्याची योग्य पद्धत | जिभेवर विरघळतील अशे खुसखुशीत बेसन लाडू |  Besan Ladu Recipe | Crispy Besan Ladu Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Easy and Quick Besan Ladu | Diwali Faral Recipe | Diwali Special Ladu Recipe | Besan Ladu Perfect Recipe | Mouth Melting Crispy Besan Ladu | 
साहित्य | Ingredients 
वजनी प्रमाण (या प्रमाणात केल्यावर तयार लाडू १ किलो होतात) 
 • हरभरा डाळ 500 ग्रॅम | Chana dal 500 gram
 • साजूक तूप 150-200 ग्रॅम | Ghee150-200 gram
 • पिठी साखर 400 ग्रॅम | Sugar Powder 400 gram
 • वेलची पूड   ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते  |  Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे  | Bedane 

वाटीचे प्रमाण | Cup Measurements
 • हरभरा डाळ 4 कप  | Chana dal 4 cups 
 • साजूक तूप पाउण कप आणि 2 मोठे चमचे  | Ghee 3/4 Cup + 2 tbsp
 • पिठी साखर 2 कप | Sugar Powder 2 cups 
 • वेलची पूड ½ चमचा | Cardamom Powder ½ tsp 
 • पिस्ते | Pistachios 
 • बेदाणे | Bedane 
 • 
To make Besan Aata 

 • Saute chana dal for 10 to 12 minutes till it changes in light golden colour. 
 • After cooling grind all. 

Besan Ladu Recipe 

 • On low heat, Saute chana dal to the kadhai.  
 • After 2 to 3 minutes, add remaining ghee and saute for 20 to 22 minutes till its get light golden colour. 

 • After 20 minutes, sprinkle 2 tsp of water / milk, saute for 2 minutes and let them cool down. 
 • After cooling add sugar powder, cardamom powder, bedane and make all the ladu. 

Other Recipes 

1/2 किलो रव्याचे परफेक्ट खुसखुशीत पाकातले रवा लाडू| पाक चुकल्यास वापरा या 5 टिप्स Rava Ladoo Marathi
https://youtu.be/6HVj_CseLgQ?si=dT15QQ7XJ8xb2ICz

या 9 टिप्स वापरून बनवा गोल एकसारखी बूंदी आणि आतपर्यंत पाक मुरलेले खुसखुशीत बुंदीचे लाडू। bundi ladu
https://youtu.be/R1O7aYKchEQ?si=Mg3RUnDt5iTV_jcb

सर्वात सोप्या पद्धतीने या 5 टिप्स वापरून बनवा बिनापाकाचे रवा बेसन लाडू 1/2 किलो प्रमाणात Besan Ladoo
https://youtu.be/OFVQR0XmwcU?si=1qoL9kufLycb08u2

1/2 वाटी तुपात गव्हाच्या पिठाचे खुसखुशीत दाणेदार चुरमा लाडू | Churma Ladu Recipe Saritas Kitchen
https://youtu.be/Zd5NZedFPNs?si=XRT66kK03oKNrWK8

कोणतेही महाग सामान न वापरता जगातील सगळ्यात पौष्टिक खुसखुशीत लाडू, घरातील उपलब्ध सामानात। Poushtik La
https://youtu.be/az_lStcS5Ek?si=uTeuIaErs7FF6zf0

दिवाळीसाठी 1 कप बेसनाचे ½Kg मोतीचूर लाडू| मार्केटसारखा मोतीचूर बनवण्याची परफेक्ट रेसिपी MotichurLadu
https://youtu.be/RnexeXfdfsA?si=LdmMjmmKjteB1xAj

डिंकाचे लाडू। या खास टिप्स, सर्वात सोप्पी पद्धत वापरून बनवा मिश्रण कोरडे न होता परफेक्ट डिंकाचे लाडू
https://youtu.be/C1WXKOuNF7U?si=pPwRBWLEEF8gBiDD

गणेशोत्सव स्पेशल, गव्हाच्या पिठाचे दाणेदार, खुसखुशीत लाडू/ लाडू विक्रीसाठी परफेक्ट 1 किलोचे प्रमाण
https://youtu.be/8xlbaup4D00?si=t4RF8NadZd1u3auT

snippet.title: Gir Pade Bapuji | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3903 | Full Episode | 16 Oct 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3903: Babita Ki Dost
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal finally wakes up early and leaves for work, but on the way, he clashes with Champaklal, and Champaklal falls down. Jetha tells Champaklal that he was caught reading his phone's text messages, so he didn't notice him coming. Champaklal taunts Jetha, saying that he was also reading his newspaper and was engrossed in it. Later, Popatlal gets happy when he sees that Babita has a special visitor. He escorts her to Babita's house, postponing his work. Who is Babita's companion Popatlal taking an interest in?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episode No - 3903
Produced By - Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Click here to watch all the episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:  https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

Minecraft But I Met Baby Herobrine is a comedic Minecraft video about a baby Herobrine who meets a player. Baby Herobrine is innocent and misguided, and the player helps him learn about the world around him. This video is sure to make you laugh!
